==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: amarelle
<hw>amarelle</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fr>1</fr> <def>any of
several varieties of cultivated sour cherry trees of the species
<spn>Prunus cerasus</spn> bearing fruit with colorless juice, e.g.
<spn>Prunus cerasus</spn> <varn>caproniana</varn>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a pale red sour cherry with colorless or nearly
colorless juice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Amarine</ent>⟦br⟧
